{
  "stem": "5644.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I got a write-up in the book about her happening.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she wrote to me that she received it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My family disappeared completed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was killed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Killed.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "99% Inside.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one brother and a sister went to the Hotel Polski.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know if you had heard about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had been killed in one of the camps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they registered themselves-- they registered themselves for America instead of Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Israelis-- the people which registered in Hotel Polski for Israel, most of them are alive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hotel Polski, after the-- you know, after-- during still the resident in the ghetto-- or-- or a little bit--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm talking '43.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans made a new trick with Jewish people together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With Jewish Gestapo people-- working with the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They made the Hotel Polski.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You never heard of it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They, they made the Hotel Polski hotel where the invite all the Jews to come freely to the hotel and they'd be exchanged for Germans overseas.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So a lot of Jews being tired of being on the Christian side, not having money, or people with a lot of money, thought themselves that's a good thing.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We advised them, the underground, as much as we could, to tell them that's not so.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That that's a new trick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "ZOB advised them that's a new trick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But to no avail.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They did it and they went there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My brother and my sister went there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And wrote me a letter to my place where I'd been hiding on the Christian side by that time to come to-- to come there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the Aryan side.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And nobody was even touched in the street-- a Jew-- if you said, I am going to Hotel Polski.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
